title: Dragons Den CA S13E04 - 'Behind the Scenes' Special (720p)
description: Dragons' Den is an internationally franchised reality television program which began in Japan. The Canadian show debuted on October 3, 2006. It is broadcast on the CBC Television Network and is hosted by Dianne Buckner. Aspiring Canadian entrepreneurs pitch business and investment ideas to a panel of six venture capitalists (called 'Dragons') in the hope of securing business financing and partnerships. Enjoy!
